  dialogueName: Intro
  type: 0
  lines:
  - text: Welcome, bartender.
  - text: I've got a little challenge for you.
  - text: 'Your job is simple: get me completely drunk.'
  - text: If you manage it, every coin in my purse is yours.
  - text: But if you fail...
  - text: ...you won't get a single coin.
  - text: Let's see if you've got what it takes.
